76561198010549421,Recommended,248820,10853069,"Posted: 26 June, 2014",all,Orpheus,"Risk of rain is a fiendishly difficult 2d shooter with roguelike inspirations. The game starts out fairly simple, you're on an alien planet, and need to find a teleporter. The first stage of the game is not too rough, however, as time progresses, regardless of your progress, enemies begin to ramp up in number and strength. This creates a dilemna, do you throughly search a level for items and monsters to kill for experience? Or do you rush the teleporter, fight the boss, and move on quickly? It's these decisions along with many fun characters to experiment playing with that make Risk of Rain shine. If you're a fan of 2D shooters, or roguelikes and don't mind dying many times over in many situations, definitely make time for this game."
