,Recommended,248820,20195279,"Posted: 1 January, 2016",all,Gativrek,"Risk of Rain is a platformer alien shooter made by Hoopoo Games. The game isn't updated so often anymore, but it's still worth buying. It has fast paced shooting with a variety of characters, beatifully made pixel graphics and a lot of items. It has simplistic controls that change with every character, having strategy involved and smart thinking during fights.The game consists on a outsider crashing into a planet, where we must use teleporters to get to a new ship that Providence guards. So you must fight through levels, finding teleporters and fighting the boss that guards it. All characters have 4 attacks, having a regular attack with no cooldown, usually a more powerful AoE, a support attack and a powerful attack with a lot of cooldown.The graphics and music aren't the best, but combined they great an amazing atmosphere. Not much more can be said about this game, it's lots of fun and easy to start playing and get into, but require learning what every enemy does, learning all the advantages for each character and learning what each item does. Just all around great game, but with it's flaws, like the few bugfixes it gets.8.5/10"
