,Recommended,248820,7753231,"Posted: 25 November, 2013",all,CharlieWoo,"Fun little roguelike platformer.Kill enemies to get coins and exp. Level up and buy chests for random loot with often times for crazy effects. The longer you take the stronger enemies get. Die and start over with nothing. Multiple classes and lots of items with randomized drops keep this game interesting. Play with your friends and you need to manage items between you and them to maximize your character's effectiveness in your group while also not leaving yourself or your friends too weak without items to survive or help deal damage late game.The game escalates in difficulty pretty quickly so the first 10-15minutes of your characters play is cruical for its post game survivability. My only gripe with this game is once you DO get the items you need it becomes pretty easy. But getting to that point takes some experience in learning how the ai works, how the difficulty scales, and how to manage your time in the most efficient manner.I've had this game for about four days and I've put twenty hours in to it. I feel like I have gotten my ten dollars worth already and will keep playing to unlock new items and characters so it's only going to get better.  Go get it!"
