,Not Recommended,248820,15992181,"Posted: 24 May, 2015",all,AWd _ (offline for a long time),"I should have done this review a long time ago, haven't played this for ages, i had to explain to a friend why this game is bad, then i remembered i hadn't a review, here is the copypaste:I have beaten 100% of it, it is actually horrible, i will put in bullet points for easier reading:-Every class besides commando and bandit are horrible, the metagame is run fast and shoot while jumping.-Without glass artifact every enemy is a meatshield.-There are only 1 secret and 3 easter eggs, easter eggs are just useless references.-The game is actually filled with bugs and exploits.-Made in gamemaker, the hitboxes glitch sometimes and decrease fps. (yes i tested a lot of mechanics, the game is really easy to break)-Sometimes the level is just not solid and you fall through it, or it has a giant invisible wall simply blocking half of the map, if you get this glitch your run is just over.-The music is interesting the first time you listen. Every time you get to the portal it play 1 of 3~ musics, after one loop you are already sick of it.-When you use command artifact, pressing E and choosing an item locks your movement, so you are a sitting duck if there are multiple items, most noticeable when using shrines.-Oh and i almost forgot the most infuriating of all: ENEMIES SPAWN UNDER YOUR FEET AND IF IT IS A STRONG ENEMY YOU GET INSTAKILLED FROM HIS ATTACK.(glass artifact on, stop walking for ONE second, enemy spawn and attack, dead. Really great game design there /sarcasm. One simple distance limit for enemy spawning would fix this, nope forget the basics again.)Multiplayer:-NETCODE is unstable, the more entities are on host's pc the bigger the chance of losing packets of data, making ghost enemies on clients games.-Ghost enemies prevent the client from activating the portal, so if the last surviving player gets a ghost enemy, then the run for the entire party is over.-There is no way to connect to a game after it starts, so if you disconnect for some reason then bye bye all progress lost.-If a player disconnects by a timeout, then a ghost player keeps connected to the server always dying and sucking xp and money every stage.-Ready button on lobby is inconsistent and sometimes unready players for no reason, more players connected the bigger the chance of glitching.-You don't need hamachi, you just need to port fowarding. and that is a negative for some people who can't and have to rely on Hamachi or other VPN.-No master server list nor steam integration, you have to manually write your friend's ip. You can't even paste your clipboard into the game.-It gets a 75% discount every godamm steam sale, and even 4packs on humble bundle for lower average.EDIT: Holy♥♥♥♥♥♥ i just checked the reviews, 95% of 13.000 are positive jokes, the humble bundle really did increased the playerbase, by a lot, and still nobody noticed any problems?"
