,Recommended,248820,7908907,"Posted: 4 December, 2013",all,crowbar,"8/10Im only like 3 hours in the game and I can already say that this game is awesome. It is easily one of the best rogue-likes at the moment, it does everything right. The Combat is fun as hell. The reason for that is the sounddesign. When you have some items and lets say 2 drones and shoot shoot 10 different types of enemies, everything has their own sound and it just sounds so damn good. And when the enemies die and drop some coins and stuff it just feels really satisfying.There are a lot of items and the cool thing is you can pick up one item several times to increase its effects, also there are active items which give you another ability.Every character has 4 abilitys which makes them unique and also drastically changes the way you have to play. Now I only have 2 characters, but there are like 10 more. With more characters I think you will have a lot of variation.The enemy design is extremely well made and there are a lot of different types of enemies. The bosses feel like how a boss should feel and when you defeat them you really feel like you achieved something.And then there is also local and online Coop, didnt tried it yet, but every game gets better with coop, and singleplayer is already fun as hell.In short, if you are a fan of Rogue-Likes or 2D Platformers, BUY THIS GAME!"
