76561197996231767,Recommended,248820,28799732,"Posted: 29 December, 2016",all,Phroedde,"This game delivers simple elegance from it's fabulous pixel art to the fantastic ambient soundtrack. Yes, it can be brutal, and yes it can be unfair, but it's marked rogue-like for a reason. With 4 moves plus a optional use item, Risk of Rain delivers gameplay that is quick and simple, yet surprisingly strategic. Manage your cooldowns and choose your attacks carefully or you will be taunted. Use your time wisely, or that next boss might be tougher than all those shiny pick-ups.With a sizeable crew of unlockable characters and a wide array of unlockable items, it'll keep you saying ""Just one more round!"" It gets even better when you round up some friends for coop and pit your squad against an army of alien threats.This game is a retro throwback. Tough gameplay, little plot and simple graphics, but beautifully combined. Take the time to read the item and monster logs and you'll see this game is more than it first appears."
