,Recommended,248820,9844508,"Posted: 17 April, 2014",all,DJ Masterson,"Welcome to A**♥♥♥♥♥♥Planet. Population: Every concievable thing in the universe that wants you dead.A FANTASTIC action-platformer combined with a roguelike experience, this game will PUNISH you. It's primary feature is it's timer, which counts up from the moment the game begins. As the timer reaches certain points, the game's overall difficulty increases. This means more (and stronger) enemies will spawn to challenge you, so this is literally a race against time!Start with the simple but effective Commando, unlock up to 9 more characters including (but not limited to), a Sniper, an Alien, and a Robot!Run across brilliantly designed and semi-randomized stages and map layouts! Jump and dodge through waves and hordes and swarms of brutal enemies! Fight! Power through foes with your innate skills, and become more powerful via the various artifacts, some of which have incredible powers! Collect gold from fallen enemies to purchase MORE artifacts, but don't linger in the same stage too long... time is laughing at you!!!You may hear some people nag about the multiplayer. It's actually much easier to beat the game with 2 or even just ONE friend. Despite having to share loot, having an extra hand is always a bonus. I highly recommend ONLY playing with good friends you can coordinate with, though. Public groups can be unreliable, trolling, or just plain not sync well with your style."
