,Recommended,248820,13109075,"Posted: 27 November, 2014",all,Billco Tabarnak!,"This retro-styled game is extremely addictive!  It's a rather difficult platform shooter, a bit like if ""The Bindinc of Isaac"" were reimagined as a platformer.  You can choose from about a dozen classes, many of which you must unlock through gameplay challenges, and each one has completely different attacks and abilities.Killing enemies gives you money, which you then use to unlock chests containing a huge variety of items that enhance your character in various ways.  Some may boost your attacking power, others give you defenses or mobility, and a few rare items have unique effects like stopping time, flying, or increasing the money you get from kills.  There are lots of secrets and remote areas only accessible with certain characters, or jetpacks, or other combinations of items, so there's always something cool to discover with each random playthrough.The enemies get stronger and more numerous as time passes, so the action starts off easy then ramps up to insane fights with you kiting nearly 100 enemies, each with their own unique attacks and behaviours.You will die.  You will learn.  You will get ridiculously good.  You will read the wiki.  And you will have a RIOT playing it."
